RQs

RQ: What are the differences in segmentability between CDS and ADS?

  • lm(f_score ~ algo * type * Unit)

RQ: How do corpus properties affect word segmentation?

  • lm(f_score ~ proportion_of_single_word_utt * algo * Unit + phrase_s * algo * Unit + word_s * algo * Unit + each_mattr * algo * Unit + each_entropy * algo * Unit + proportion_of_hapaxes_words * algo * Unit + algo * Unit, data = dflmregialgo)

RQ: Do corpus properties of CDS differ from those of ADS in Korean? (controlling for corpus size)

Modeling on each corpus property respectively:

  • lm(values ~ type * each_words_tokens)

RQs

RQ: How do corpus properties affect word segmentation?

  • lm(f_score ~ proportion_of_single_word_utt + phrase_s + word_s + each_mattr + each_entropy + proportion_of_hapaxes_words + algo * type * Unit + type * each_words_tokens, data = dflmregialgo)
    • corpus properties = proportion_of_single_word_utt + phrase_s + word_s + each_mattr + each_entropy + proportion_of_hapaxes_words
    • algo * type * Unit for checking main effects whether are cancalled out by corpus properties
    • type * each_words_tokens for controlling the effect of corpus size and register (is this neccessary? if the purpose is to observe the effect of corpus properties independent of corpus properties?)
